OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with long clear spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping, especially over Argyll and
OL,8,FBute. Remaining dry overnight with
OL,9,Fplenty of clear spells. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA dry morning with long spells
OL,12,Fof sunshine, especially near western
OL,13,Fcoasts. Turning cloudy in the
OL,14,Fafternoon with the odd shower possible
OL,15,Fin the east, staying dry towards the
OL,16,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
